{"tid":1530174,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無罷工嘅人你哋同港豬冇分別","createTime":"2019-09-02T01:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T06:49:26.000Z","uid":275109,"like":40,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"3c459af4e97f7ab686651205612d45790ab707bb","tid":1530174,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"今日已經係反送中運動嘅第84日<br />\n<br />\n手足傷得嘅就傷，拉得嘅都拉左800幾個<br />\n831 太子站俾人爆頭打到流晒血，暈左係地嘅仲生死未卜<br />\n<br />\n如果你係支持呢一場運動，有咩理由驅使你唔罷工？<br />\n可能你會覺得罷工無用，但我想講罷工係表態嘅一種方式，表明你支持呢個運動，亦都係用行動支持上前線嘅手足最安全嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得罷工會俾人炒犧牲好大，咁我問你俾人拉咗嘅義士，被子彈所傷嘅手足 佢哋嘅犧牲又算係咩？<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住等人哋幫你罷工，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工係一個自發行為，無人有義務幫你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">革命就係要有犧牲<br />\n想贏就要付出 如果你打算住坐享其成，連罷工等人幫你爭取，得罪講句你同港豬無分別</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n唔係一句口號，請用行動支持<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果今日你無罷工 聽日仲有一日機會，請你行出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hu35SwZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhu35SwZ.jpg&h=756c95a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fbe166ae5af245950d9a3d03e2df3e2c0268338","tid":1530174,"uid":275109,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:33:16.000Z","msg":"不要習慣被欺壓，我哋已經無退路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T4vLSyV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT4vLSyV.jpg&h=26966a5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac22e635a7a081c3341ae70997dfa45c8c593c01","tid":1530174,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:38:06.000Z","msg":"唔好亂傳死訊啦 要知道真相第一個方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530023</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrS2UOq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrS2UOq.png&h=af916716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一日未有受害人又或者佢屋企人企出嚟，所有人講嘅嘢都唔可以作準<br />\n有冇人識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e751046f4f6a69be20e54f61167281cc9650b234","tid":1530174,"uid":55544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:40:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記住兩日都有罷工集會</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bc40fd3075e2600ac973f5ba4786a363f91d396b","tid":1530174,"uid":275109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:44:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人可唔可以唔好咁垃圾<br />\n係咪連罷工嘅勇氣都冇？</span>"},{"pid":"78f91cc660bccd0050e76091263323751dce4968","tid":1530174,"uid":10691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:45:16.000Z","msg":"屌你地 我做生意都拎一日營業額黎罷 你地咪一張醫生紙 都唔肯 <br />\n一陣金鐘見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e00353444e58bd467882b7ee8c783f709bce08d","tid":1530174,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78f91cc660bccd0050e76091263323751dce4968","tid":1530174,"uid":10691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:45:16.000Z","msg":"屌你地 我做生意都拎一日營業額黎罷 你地咪一張醫生紙 都唔肯 <br />\n一陣金鐘見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:46:05.000Z","msg":"金鐘見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482827ece2af63c7a344b7ba6923bdc5cb38b621","tid":1530174,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:48:36.000Z","msg":"其實俾人炒 又有咩好怕（如果佢因為你罷工所以炒你 我敢肯定 你老細想炒你好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n如果運動失敗 我肯撚定 香港人嘅下場會比冇咗份工更加慘<br /