<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除非可以儲到氣好有noise咁全港再黎過, 分散既自發罷工好大機會只會畀既得利益者 (尤其藍絲人) mark實再搵藉口即時清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5414711942fdbe449fedfd8ed6a13d493bc85809","tid":1530174,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:18:19.000Z","msg":"罷左 而家去邊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc314c80669e921aac83adbe1bf19fffc8487759","tid":1530174,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:18:21.000Z","msg":"原諒我上個月淨係罷左兩日 已收warming <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd370aef0d7afba4eb0b90ecdbb632347b6ec5c","tid":1530174,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:19:36.000Z","msg":"和理非既力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係冇"},{"pid":"7eb77ba68172197ca50dcc876ce6ab5174a7761b","tid":1530174,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:19:59.000Z","msg":"和理非，好無力，好忟？<br />\n要抗爭，只有十月一前每日堅持做以下既事，係堅持，堅唔到都要堅，係呢到發誓你堅持呢個九月，就一個月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 罷消費（任何福建幫、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、藍紅食店）好難？勇武難唔難？<br />\n2. 低享樂（要發洩，做運動、十點9叫、唔好taobao消費食好野）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 每日like and share 1個文宣post<br />\n5. 下載Twitter 開acc,每日出1個post<br />\n6. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣教育自由行。<br />\n7. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n8. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n9. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n10. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n11. Tag或吹你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加，如果你咁都做唔到，講咩野好忟好惱無野可做。<br />\n只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"a09878f4a966abe6458532d94702707c2ae7f69e","tid":1530174,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:23:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ea9a213f259958bc68ebd2f